:''For other schools by this name, see: [[Sandy Creek High School]]''
'''Sandy Creek High School''' is a [[high school]] in [[Fairfield, Nebraska|Fairfield]], [[Nebraska]] ([[USA]]). A [[public school]], it currently has around 208 students.

