{{Nebraska-school-stub}}
[[category:High schools in Nebraska]]
Sandy Creek is the home of Hastings College Basketball star Kevin Prochaska. Kevin holds the all-time leading scoring record at Sandy Creek among many other records. On the weekend Kevin can be found losing fights to girls or crying. He also placed a respected 8th place in tripple jump his senior year. He enjoys to build forts with his high school buddy Clay Mach (alumni).
